org.wlf.filedownloader.base

类 FailReason

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • org.wlf.filedownloader.base.FailReason
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Serializable
    直接已知子类:
    FailException, OnRenameDownloadFileListener.RenameDownloadFileFailReason, UrlFailReason

    public abstract class FailReason
extends Exception
    fail reason, which extends Exception, it is need to care about the type(getType()) and the cause (Throwable.getCause()), and sometime may need to care about the original cause(getOriginalCause())
    失败原因类，扩展自Exception类，使用时一般只需要关心失败类型(getType())和失败原因(Throwable.getCause())即可，有时候可能还需要关心原始的失败原因 (getOriginalCause())，可以满足各种同步和异步场合需求
    作者:
    wlf(Andy)
    另请参阅:
